I'll help you organize a team to create the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway website with CLI features integrated into a web dashboard, including SMS statistics by users. Let me assign appropriate tasks to my team members.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.append_task",
        "args": {
            "task_id": "1",
            "dependent_task_ids": [],
            "instruction": "Create a PRD for the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway website. Include requirements for CLI features integration, web dashboard functionality, and SMS statistics tracking by users. Research existing Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway capabilities and CLI features that need to be implemented in the web interface.",
            "assignee": "Emma",
            "task_type": ""
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.append_task",
        "args": {
            "task_id": "2",
            "dependent_task_ids": ["1"],
            "instruction": "Design the system architecture for the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web interface. Include components for CLI command execution, user management, dashboard interface, and SMS statistics visualization. Specify integration points with the Jasmin SMPP gateway backend.",
            "assignee": "Bob",
            "task_type": ""
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.append_task",
        "args": {
            "task_id": "3",
            "dependent_task_ids": ["2"],
            "instruction": "Develop the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web application with all CLI features integrated into the dashboard, user management, and SMS statistics tracking. Implement the solution based on the PRD and system architecture. Ensure the project can be easily deployed to GitHub.",
            "assignee": "Alex",
            "task_type": ""
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "TeamLeader.publish_team_message",
        "args": {
            "content": "Please create a comprehensive PRD for a Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web interface. The website should provide a dashboard that integrates all CLI features of the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway and includes SMS statistics tracking by user. Research all CLI features of Jasmin SMPP Gateway thoroughly to ensure all functionality is represented in the web interface. The final product will need to be published to the user's GitHub account.",
            "send_to": "Emma"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "I've created a development plan for your Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway website project and assigned the initial task to Emma, our Product Manager. She'll research Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway capabilities and create a comprehensive Product Requirements Document that outlines all CLI features that need to be integrated into the web dashboard, along with the SMS statistics tracking functionality by users.\n\nOnce Emma completes her analysis, Bob will design the system architecture, and Alex will develop the web application. We'll ensure that all CLI features are properly represented in the web interface and that the final product includes robust SMS statistics tracking. When the project is complete, we'll help you publish it to your GitHub account.\n\nI'll keep you updated on our progress throughout the development process."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I'll finish Emma's task and move on to Bob's task in our plan.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.finish_current_task",
        "args": {}
    },
    {
        "command_name": "TeamLeader.publish_team_message",
        "args": {
            "content": "Based on Emma's PRD for the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web interface, please design the system architecture for this project. Your architecture should include components for CLI command execution, user management, dashboard interface, and SMS statistics visualization. Be sure to specify the integration points with the Jasmin SMPP gateway backend. The architecture should support all the features outlined in the PRD, particularly ensuring all CLI features are accessible through the web dashboard and that SMS statistics can be tracked by user.",
            "send_to": "Bob"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "I've marked Emma's PRD task as complete and assigned Bob to design the system architecture for the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web interface. Bob will now work on designing the components for CLI command execution, user management, dashboard interface, and SMS statistics visualization, along with specifying how the web interface will integrate with the Jasmin SMPP gateway backend. Once Bob completes the architecture design, Alex will begin development of the actual web application."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I'll mark Bob's task as complete and move on to the next task in our plan.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.finish_current_task",
        "args": {}
    },
    {
        "command_name": "TeamLeader.publish_team_message",
        "args": {
            "content": "Based on the PRD by Emma and the system architecture designed by Bob, please develop the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web application. Your implementation should integrate all CLI features into the dashboard, include comprehensive user management functionality, and implement SMS statistics tracking by user. The architecture documents can be found in the workspace directory:\n\n1. System Design Document: '../workspace/jasmin_smpp_web_dashboard_system_design.md'\n2. Class Diagram: '../workspace/jasmin_smpp_web_dashboard_class_diagram.mermaid'\n3. Sequence Diagram: '../workspace/jasmin_smpp_web_dashboard_sequence_diagram.mermaid'\n\nPlease ensure the project is well-structured and documented so it can be easily deployed to the user's GitHub account when completed.",
            "send_to": "Alex"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "I've marked Bob's architecture design task as complete. Bob has created several important deliverables for your Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway web interface project, including a detailed system design document, class diagrams, and sequence diagrams.\n\nI've now assigned Alex to begin development of the actual web application based on Emma's PRD and Bob's architecture. Alex will implement the web dashboard that integrates all CLI features of the Jasmin SMPP SMS Gateway, includes user management functionality, and provides SMS statistics tracking by user. Once development is complete, we'll help you publish the repository to your GitHub account."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I need to check the code for errors that are preventing the Jasmin SMPP dashboard from opening. Let me examine the project files and identify any issues that could be causing the problem.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.append_task",
        "args": {
            "task_id": "1",
            "dependent_task_ids": [],
            "instruction": "Analyze the current code for the Jasmin SMPP dashboard, identify errors preventing the website from opening at https://jasmin-smpp-dashboard-xmbko-015rz-78c28e.mgx.dev, and prepare a fix for these issues.",
            "assignee": "Alex",
            "task_type": ""
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "TeamLeader.publish_team_message",
        "args": {
            "content": "The Jasmin SMPP dashboard website is not opening at https://jasmin-smpp-dashboard-xmbko-015rz-78c28e.mgx.dev. Please examine the code in the current directory (/data/chats/015rz/workspace), identify any errors that could be preventing the site from loading, and implement fixes. Focus on potential issues like routing problems, server configuration errors, entry point issues, or deployment configuration problems. Once you've identified the issues, please provide a detailed explanation of what was wrong and the fixes you've implemented.",
            "send_to": "Alex"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "I understand there's an issue with the Jasmin SMPP dashboard not opening at the provided URL. I've asked Alex to analyze the code in the workspace to identify and fix errors preventing the website from loading. Alex will look for potential problems in routing, server configuration, entry points, or deployment settings, and will provide a detailed explanation of the issues found and fixes implemented. I'll update you once Alex has completed the analysis and implemented the necessary fixes."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I need to mark the task as completed since Alex has finished analyzing and fixing the code for the Jasmin SMPP dashboard. I'll also provide an update to the user about the resolution.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.finish_current_task",
        "args": {}
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "Good news! Alex has identified and fixed the issues with your Jasmin SMPP dashboard. The problems included React Router v7 compatibility issues, component naming conflicts, and import/provider configuration errors. The fixes have been implemented in the App.jsx and AuthContext.jsx files.\n\nYour dashboard should now be working correctly at a new URL: https://jasmin-smpp-dashboard-xmbko-015rz-ff70c0.mgx.dev\n\nPlease check if you can access the dashboard now. Let me know if you need any further assistance with the application or if you'd like Alex to implement additional features like real-time message tracking, improved authentication, or enhanced SMS statistics visualizations."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I'll help organize another code review and fix for the Jasmin SMPP dashboard. Let me create a new task for Alex to thoroughly review and prepare production-ready code.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.append_task",
        "args": {
            "task_id": "1",
            "dependent_task_ids": [],
            "instruction": "Perform a comprehensive code review of the Jasmin SMPP dashboard, fix all remaining errors, and prepare production-ready code. This includes:\n1. Review and fix all React components\n2. Ensure proper error handling\n3. Implement proper authentication flow\n4. Add loading states\n5. Optimize performance\n6. Add proper documentation\n7. Set up proper environment configurations\n8. Implement proper logging\nDeliver the final production-ready code with deployment instructions.",
            "assignee": "Alex",
            "task_type": ""
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "TeamLeader.publish_team_message",
        "args": {
            "content": "Por favor, realiza una revisión exhaustiva del código del dashboard Jasmin SMPP en el directorio '/data/chats/015rz/workspace'. Necesitamos que el código esté listo para producción, por lo que debes:\n\n1. Revisar y corregir todos los componentes React\n2. Implementar manejo de errores adecuado\n3. Asegurar que el flujo de autenticación funcione correctamente\n4. Agregar estados de carga\n5. Optimizar el rendimiento\n6. Añadir documentación apropiada\n7. Configurar correctamente los ambientes\n8. Implementar logging adecuado\n\nPor favor, entrega el código final listo para producción junto con las instrucciones de implementación.",
            "send_to": "Alex"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "He asignado a Alex la tarea de realizar una revisión exhaustiva del código del dashboard Jasmin SMPP. Se enfocará en preparar un código completamente listo para producción, incluyendo la corrección de todos los errores, implementación de manejo de errores adecuado, optimización del rendimiento, y documentación completa. Te mantendré informado cuando Alex complete la revisión y tengamos el código listo para producción."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I need to mark Alex's task as complete and update the user with details about the code review and fixes.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.finish_current_task",
        "args": {}
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "Alex ha completado la revisión exhaustiva del código y ha realizado las siguientes mejoras:\n\n1. Se ha mejorado el servicio API con manejo de errores y validación de tokens\n2. Se implementó mejor seguridad con verificación de expiración de tokens\n3. Se agregaron estados de carga y límites de error en toda la aplicación\n4. Se integró gestión de estado con Redux\n\nLos archivos actualizados incluyen:\n- /src/services/api.js - Servicio API mejorado\n- /src/App.jsx - Protección de rutas mejorada\n- /src/components/common/LoadingSpinner.jsx - Nuevo componente de carga\n- /src/contexts/AuthContext.jsx - Contexto de autenticación mejorado\n\nLa aplicación está disponible en: https://jasmin-smpp-dashboard-xmbko-015rz-ff70c0.mgx.dev\n\nPor favor, pruebe la aplicación y hágame saber si encuentra algún otro problema o si necesita ajustes adicionales."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

I'll create a new task for Alex to push the code to GitHub, including proper documentation and setup instructions.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "Plan.append_task",
        "args": {
            "task_id": "2",
            "dependent_task_ids": [],
            "instruction": "Create a GitHub repository and push the Jasmin SMPP dashboard code. Include:\n1. Complete source code from /data/chats/015rz/workspace\n2. README.md with setup and deployment instructions\n3. .gitignore file\n4. Environment configuration examples\n5. Documentation for API endpoints and features\n6. License file",
            "assignee": "Alex",
            "task_type": ""
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "TeamLeader.publish_team_message",
        "args": {
            "content": "Please create a GitHub repository for the Jasmin SMPP dashboard code located in /data/chats/015rz/workspace. Ensure to include:\n1. All source code\n2. Comprehensive README.md with setup and deployment instructions\n3. Proper .gitignore file\n4. Environment configuration examples\n5. API documentation\n6. License file\n\nPlease provide the GitHub repository URL once completed.",
            "send_to": "Alex"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.reply_to_human",
        "args": {
            "content": "I've assigned Alex to create a GitHub repository for the Jasmin SMPP dashboard code. The repository will include complete source code, documentation, setup instructions, and configuration examples. Alex will provide the GitHub repository URL once it's ready."
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

Since we need to get the GitHub repository URL from the user before Alex can proceed, I'll ask the user for this information.

```json
[
    {
        "command_name": "RoleZero.ask_human",
        "args": {
            "question": "To proceed with pushing the code to GitHub, we need the target GitHub repository URL. Could you please provide:\n1. The GitHub repository URL where you'd like the code to be pushed, or\n2. Your GitHub username if you'd like us to create a new repository for you?"
        }
    },
    {
        "command_name": "end"
    }
]
```

